#compdef diskusage
# Documentation: https://github.com/dmytro/zsh-compdef/blob/master/_diskusage
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-17
# Verified: upstream docs at the URL above.
# Source: dmytro/zsh-compdef (_diskusage).

_arguments -s \
  '(- *)-h[display help]' \
  '(-c)-c[config file]:config:_files' \
  '(-o)-o[output template]:template:' \
  '*-d[additional template key=values]:template:' \
  '-x[skip mounts with different device numbers]' \
  '*:directory:_directories'
